sentences.sentence: People on the road didn′t know what happened and said, "Look at the young man. He is riding a tiger! Cool! Superman!" Hearing these words, the young man was very angry, "Why can′t they see I′m suffering a lot?"
sentences.translation: 路上的人不知道发生了什么，说：“看那个年轻人。他骑着一只老虎！酷！超人！”听到这些话，年轻人非常生气。“为什么他们看不出我在受苦？”
